Dialogue: 0,0:01:46.04,0:01:47.59,SoraNoWoto,,0000,0000,0000,,There...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:01.05,0:02:02.51,SoraNoWoto,,0000,0000,0000,,Autumn's here.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:08.73,0:02:11.90,SoraNoWoto,,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(640,700)}So your father was a tanker, Kureha-chan?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:11.90,0:02:12.57,SoraNoWoto,,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(640,700)}Yep.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:12.57,0:02:14.89,SoraNoWoto,,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(640,700)}With just six Type-2 Millipads,
Dialogue: 0,0:02:14.89,0:02:17.32,SoraNoWoto,,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(640,700)}he led more than a thousand citizens and soldiers...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:17.32,0:02:20.70,SoraNoWoto,,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(640,700)}...out from the completely surrounded Wardenburk.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:21.66,0:02:24.66,SoraNoWoto,,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(640,700)}He was the hero of the legendary "Strategy of Retrieval".
Dialogue: 0,0:02:26.20,0:02:27.25,SoraNoWoto,,0000,0000,0000,,Incredible.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:27.25,0:02:28.37,SoraNoWoto,,0000,0000,0000,,Right?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:28.37,0:02:32.17,SoraNoWoto,,0000,0000,0000,,And when he got wounded during that mission,
Dialogue: 0,0:02:32.17,0:02:36.17,SoraNoWoto,,0000,0000,0000,,he met my mother who was a medic where he was hospitalized.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:36.17,0:02:39.13,SoraNoWoto,,0000,0000,0000,,And the baby born from them...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:40.30,0:02:42.14,SoraNoWoto,,0000,0000,0000,,...was you?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:42.14,0:02:43.05,SoraNoWoto,,0000,0000,0000,,That's right!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:45.14,0:02:47.18,SoraNoWoto,,0000,0000,0000,,No! I'm not a potato!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:47.18,0:02:50.31,SoraNoWoto,,0000,0000,0000,,My, what a splendid potato.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:50.69,0:02:53.19,SoraNoWoto,,0000,0000,0000,,This is thanks to your care, Kana-chan.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:55.82,0:02:59.90,SoraNoWoto,,0000,0000,0000,,We probably have enough to share some with the townspeople.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:59.90,0:03:02.95,SoraNoWoto,,0000,0000,0000,,And Claus-san should be coming by.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:03.70,0:03:05.70,SoraNoWoto,,0000,0000,0000,,Let's give some to him as gift.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:06.12,0:03:07.50,SoraNoWoto,,0000,0000,0000,,He's coming?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:07.95,0:03:11.42,SoraNoWoto,,0000,0000,0000,,You really like him, don't you Kureha-chan?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:12.12,0:03:15.50,SoraNoWoto,,0000,0000,0000,,R-Rather than like, I look up to him.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:15.50,0:03:16.50,SoraNoWoto,,0000,0000,0000,,Poke.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:36.90,0:03:38.32,SoraNoWoto,,0000,0000,0000,,Rio-senpai...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:40.78,0:03:42.53,SoraNoWoto,,0000,0000,0000,,So she can do that too?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:42.53,0:03:44.91,SoraNoWoto,,0000,0000,0000,,That's Rio-senpai for you.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:44.91,0:03:45.87,SoraNoWoto,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:54.38,0:03:56.88,SoraNoWoto,,0000,0000,0000,,The wind is getting stronger.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:58.88,0:04:02.76,SoraNoWoto,,0000,0000,0000,,It looks like the weather's getting worse, so let's finish up and get inside.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:02.76,0:04:03.55,SoraNoWoto,,0000,0000,0000,,Roger!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:03.55,0:04:04.43,SoraNoWoto,,0000,0000,0000,,Roger.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:04.43,0:04:05.50,SoraNoWoto,,0000,0000,0000,,You too, Noel-chan.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:05.51,0:04:06.34,SoraNoWoto,,0000,0000,0000,,Okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:17.07,0:04:17.90,SoraNoWoto,,0000,0000,0000,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:18.29,0:04:22.11,SoraNoWoto,,0000,0000,0000,,Like I said, Rio-senpai seemed weird, didn't she?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:22.11,0:04:22.90,SoraNoWoto,,0000,0000,0000,,For example?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:23.45,0:04:25.11,SoraNoWoto,,0000,0000,0000,,Like that trumpet playing.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:25.11,0:04:27.41,SoraNoWoto,,0000,0000,0000,,That was wonderful and cool, wasn't it?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:28.08,0:04:29.91,SoraNoWoto,,0000,0000,0000,,She didn't seem to be in high spirits.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:29.91,0:04:32.79,SoraNoWoto,,0000,0000,0000,,Doesn't she usually avoid small talk?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:33.16,0:04:34.17,SoraNoWoto,,0000,0000,0000,,But...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:34.17,0:04:35.42,SoraNoWoto,,0000,0000,0000,,Ah, the dinner!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:35.42,0:04:37.79,SoraNoWoto,,0000,0000,0000,,The tempura was delicious, wasn't it?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:37.79,0:04:40.80,SoraNoWoto,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah, the potato was so soft.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:40.80,0:04:41.80,SoraNoWoto,,0000,0000,0000,,Not that!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:47.26,0:04:49.93,SoraNoWoto,,0000,0000,0000,,Here, Rio. While it's still warm.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:49.93,0:04:52.22,SoraNoWoto,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah. Thanks.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:55.81,0:04:56.94,SoraNoWoto,,0000,0000,0000,,Is it good?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:56.94,0:04:57.86,SoraNoWoto,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:57.86,0:04:59.86,SoraNoWoto,,0000,0000,0000,,Really? Glad to hear it.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:03.11,0:05:04.07,SoraNoWoto,,0000,0000,0000,,The green pepper!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:04.07,0:05:06.20,SoraNoWoto,,0000,0000,0000,,She chewed it like it was nothing!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:06.20,0:05:08.51,SoraNoWoto,,0000,0000,0000,,What? {\i1}The{\i0} Rio-senpai?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:08.51,0:05:09.25,SoraNoWoto,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:09.25,0:05:16.42,SoraNoWoto,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}The{\i0} Rio-senpai that would always pick them out no matter how finely chopped and set them aside.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:16.42,0:05:19.59,SoraNoWoto,,0000,0000,0000,,That... is pretty serious.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:30.85,0:05:31.47,SoraNoWoto,,0000,0000,0000,,Poke.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:34.14,0:05:34.98,SoraNoWoto,,0000,0000,0000,,Hm?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:39.61,0:05:41.65,SoraNoWoto,,0000,0000,0000,,Is this Claus-san?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:41.65,0:05:43.44,SoraNoWoto,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah! It's my treasure!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:43.98,0:05:46.45,SoraNoWoto,,0000,0000,0000,,The Desert Wolf, Miracle Claus!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:46.99,0:05:51.28,SoraNoWoto,,0000,0000,0000,,He has the 481st Platoon's symbol of unity and glory, a wolf's head,
Dialogue: 0,0:05:51.28,0:05:53.04,SoraNoWoto,,0000,0000,0000,,tattooed on his left chest.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:53.62,0:05:55.33,SoraNoWoto,,0000,0000,0000,,It's so cool, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:55.33,0:05:56.79,SoraNoWoto,,0000,0000,0000,,You can't have it.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:00.17,0:06:02.80,SoraNoWoto,,0000,0000,0000,,I don't think we need to worry too much.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:03.80,0:06:07.51,SoraNoWoto,,0000,0000,0000,,We worried too much about the Captain the other day, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:10.43,0:06:13.72,SoraNoWoto,,0000,0000,0000,,After all, it's Rio-senpai we're talking about.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:13.72,0:06:16.43,SoraNoWoto,,0000,0000,0000,,She's so cool, striking and beautiful.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:16.77,0:06:22.82,SoraNoWoto,,0000,0000,0000,,Right. She must have conquered her hate of green peppers, and now she can eat them.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:22.82,0:06:26.69,SoraNoWoto,,0000,0000,0000,,You really like Rio-senpai, don't you Kureha-chan?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:26.72,0:06:29.91,SoraNoWoto,,0000,0000,0000,,She's the person I look up to, after all.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:29.91,0:06:32.49,SoraNoWoto,,0000,0000,0000,,Well, me too, but...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:32.49,0:06:34.41,SoraNoWoto,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, what do you think, Noel-chan?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:41.88,0:06:42.84,SoraNoWoto,,0000,0000,0000,,Poke...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:42.84,0:06:43.84,SoraNoWoto,,0000,0000,0000,,Watch out!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:54.51,0:06:56.62,SoraNoWoto,,0000,0000,0000,,Noel-chan's already sleeping.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:57.22,0:06:59.18,SoraNoWoto,,0000,0000,0000,,She's so hopeless.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:59.18,0:07:01.65,SoraNoWoto,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll give her half of my bed.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:01.65,0:07:03.53,SoraNoWoto,,0000,0000,0000,,Kanata, grab that side.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:04.36,0:07:05.23,SoraNoWoto,,0000,0000,0000,,Okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:21.71,0:07:23.13,SoraNoWoto,,0000,0000,0000,,The fire in the bath...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:23.13,0:07:25.09,SoraNoWoto,,0000,0000,0000,,You forgot to put it out.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:25.09,0:07:27.59,SoraNoWoto,,0000,0000,0000,,Sorry, I was careless.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:28.51,0:07:33.14,SoraNoWoto,,0000,0000,0000,,The way you seem to always be sharp but actually careless at times is one of your charm points,
Dialogue: 0,0:07:33.47,0:07:35.60,SoraNoWoto,,0000,0000,0000,,but you've been overdoing it lately.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:36.39,0:07:37.51,SoraNoWoto,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:39.73,0:07:43.15,SoraNoWoto,,0000,0000,0000,,Do you regret hanging up on your father?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:47.61,0:07:49.86,SoraNoWoto,,0000,0000,0000,,Well, no worries.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:49.86,0:07:53.28,SoraNoWoto,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll do something about your mistakes.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:56.41,0:08:01.21,SoraNoWoto,,0000,0000,0000,,At least, act the cool senior in front of those kids.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:06.13,0:08:07.50,SoraNoWoto,,0000,0000,0000,,Was it the wind?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:09.42,0:08:10.92,SoraNoWoto,,0000,0000,0000,,I don't think so.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:11.72,0:08:12.97,SoraNoWoto,,0000,0000,0000,,Sorry to intrude so late,
Dialogue: 0,0:08:12.97,0:08:14.30,SoraNoWoto,,0000,0000,0000,,but it's of top priority.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:14.30,0:08:16.26,SoraNoWoto,,0000,0000,0000,,Who is it for?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:16.26,0:08:20.60,SoraNoWoto,,0000,0000,0000,,1121st Platoon, Sergeant Kazumiya Rio.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:24.27,0:08:25.19,SoraNoWoto,,0000,0000,0000,,Please accept it.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:33.24,0:08:36.45,SoraNoWoto,,0000,0000,0000,,Major, please come in.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:36.45,0:08:39.70,SoraNoWoto,,0000,0000,0000,,You won't be able to travel in this weather.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:39.70,0:08:41.54,SoraNoWoto,,0000,0000,0000,,Even as the Desert Wolf.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:41.54,0:08:45.21,SoraNoWoto,,0000,0000,0000,,I told you to stop calling me that.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:45.21,0:08:46.04,SoraNoWoto,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:46.92,0:08:50.59,SoraNoWoto,,0000,0000,0000,,How about hot tea and a warm bath as an apology?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:54.84,0:08:58.10,SoraNoWoto,,0000,0000,0000,,Thanks for carrying out your mission, even in the middle of a typhoon.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:58.72,0:09:04.10,SoraNoWoto,,0000,0000,0000,,Um, I apologize that these are leftovers from last night, but please have some!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:07.98,0:09:11.86,SoraNoWoto,,0000,0000,0000,,You should have woken me up if Claus-san was coming.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:17.07,0:09:19.53,SoraNoWoto,,0000,0000,0000,,This is well made. It's good even though it's cold.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:19.53,0:09:21.70,SoraNoWoto,,0000,0000,0000,,The green peppers were grown with great care, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:21.70,0:09:23.20,SoraNoWoto,,0000,0000,0000,,Really?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:23.20,0:09:26.33,SoraNoWoto,,0000,0000,0000,,I was the one who picked and fried it.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:27.67,0:09:30.17,SoraNoWoto,,0000,0000,0000,,Looks like you'll be a good wife, Kureha.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:31.69,0:09:33.71,SoraNoWoto,,0000,0000,0000,,Is that a new newspaper?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:34.13,0:09:37.93,SoraNoWoto,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes, the Major brought it with him.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:37.93,0:09:39.89,SoraNoWoto,,0000,0000,0000,,What about the peace treaty?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:39.89,0:09:42.93,SoraNoWoto,,0000,0000,0000,,The talks are still encountering problems.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:42.93,0:09:45.02,SoraNoWoto,,0000,0000,0000,,They still haven't reached an agreement.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:45.48,0:09:50.40,SoraNoWoto,,0000,0000,0000,,If only Princess Iliya were still alive, things might have turned out differently.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:51.69,0:09:54.69,SoraNoWoto,,0000,0000,0000,,Princess... Iliya?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:55.15,0:09:57.24,SoraNoWoto,,0000,0000,0000,,You seriously don't know her?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:57.24,0:09:58.95,SoraNoWoto,,0000,0000,0000,,She was the hero of Vingt.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:58.95,0:10:02.62,SoraNoWoto,,0000,0000,0000,,The first Princess of Archduke Arkadia.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:02.99,0:10:05.41,SoraNoWoto,,0000,0000,0000,,Our Helvetian army's goddess of victory.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:05.41,0:10:09.92,SoraNoWoto,,0000,0000,0000,,She was a tanker goddess along with Claus-san, the Desert wolf.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:10.31,0:10:12.24,SoraNoWoto,,0000,0000,0000,,Kureha, about that...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:13.63,0:10:14.71,SoraNoWoto,,0000,0000,0000,,Is everyone here?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:15.09,0:10:16.38,SoraNoWoto,,0000,0000,0000,,We have an emergency!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:32.40,0:10:34.36,SoraNoWoto,,0000,0000,0000,,Rio! Rio!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:44.20,0:10:45.95,SoraNoWoto,,0000,0000,0000,,What's the ruckus?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:45.95,0:10:49.96,SoraNoWoto,,0000,0000,0000,,A kid from Yumina's place has been missing since this morning.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:49.96,0:10:51.04,SoraNoWoto,,0000,0000,0000,,Please lend us a hand.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:51.04,0:10:51.79,SoraNoWoto,,0000,0000,0000,,What?!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:51.79,0:10:53.42,SoraNoWoto,,0000,0000,0000,,Yumina-san, who's missing?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:57.55,0:10:58.92,SoraNoWoto,,0000,0000,0000,,It's Seiya-san.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:11.06,0:11:13.54,SoraNoWoto,,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(640,700)}The river's level has risen quite a bit.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:14.23,0:11:17.36,SoraNoWoto,,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(640,700)}They haven't harvested the fields downstream yet.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:18.11,0:11:20.03,SoraNoWoto,,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(640,700)}If the dam doesn't hold, it'll be ruined.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:20.78,0:11:22.78,SoraNoWoto,,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(640,700)}I don't know my way around town.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:22.78,0:11:24.37,SoraNoWoto,,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(640,700)}I'm counting on you, Kureha.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:24.37,0:11:25.58,SoraNoWoto,,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(640,700)}Roger!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:26.41,0:11:28.16,SoraNoWoto,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm truly sorry!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:28.91,0:11:31.00,SoraNoWoto,,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(640,700)}Just as I took my eyes off him...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:31.59,0:11:34.38,SoraNoWoto,,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(640,700)}Search and rescue is one of the army's responsibilities.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:34.38,0:11:35.54,SoraNoWoto,,0000,0000,0000,,Leave it to us.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:42.34,0:11:43.26,SoraNoWoto,,0000,0000,0000,,Let's go!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:43.26,0:11:44.05,SoraNoWoto,,0000,0000,0000,,Roger!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:44.47,0:11:46.31,SoraNoWoto,,0000,0000,0000,,Seiya!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:46.31,0:11:47.39,SoraNoWoto,,0000,0000,0000,,Seiya-kun!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:49.47,0:11:50.43,SoraNoWoto,,0000,0000,0000,,Seiya!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:50.43,0:11:51.81,SoraNoWoto,,0000,0000,0000,,Seiya-kun!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:00.90,0:12:02.24,SoraNoWoto,,0000,0000,0000,,Wow...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:02.24,0:12:03.57,SoraNoWoto,,0000,0000,0000,,The current's so strong.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:05.37,0:12:06.58,SoraNoWoto,,0000,0000,0000,,If he fell in there...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:13.42,0:12:14.79,SoraNoWoto,,0000,0000,0000,,Seiya!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:14.79,0:12:16.13,SoraNoWoto,,0000,0000,0000,,Seiya-kun!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:21.59,0:12:23.05,SoraNoWoto,,0000,0000,0000,,Wh-What was that?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:23.05,0:12:24.01,SoraNoWoto,,0000,0000,0000,,You!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:26.80,0:12:28.76,SoraNoWoto,,0000,0000,0000,,You know something, don't you?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:29.81,0:12:31.98,SoraNoWoto,,0000,0000,0000,,You came out here because you know where he might be, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:33.19,0:12:34.35,SoraNoWoto,,0000,0000,0000,,Spill it!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:34.35,0:12:35.65,SoraNoWoto,,0000,0000,0000,,Where's Seiya?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:39.48,0:12:40.15,SoraNoWoto,,0000,0000,0000,,The field.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:40.83,0:12:41.55,SoraNoWoto,,0000,0000,0000,,The field?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:41.55,0:12:42.58,SoraNoWoto,,0000,0000,0000,,Eggplants.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:42.58,0:12:44.91,SoraNoWoto,,0000,0000,0000,,It's Yumina onee-chan's favorite.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:45.57,0:12:49.91,SoraNoWoto,,0000,0000,0000,,That's why we gathered up our allowance...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:50.45,0:12:51.41,SoraNoWoto,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm sure Seiya...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:54.16,0:12:55.25,SoraNoWoto,,0000,0000,0000,,Where is it?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:15.02,0:13:16.31,SoraNoWoto,,0000,0000,0000,,Wai{\fscx300}-{\fscx100} Lemme{\fscx300}-
Dialogue: 0,0:13:19.73,0:13:21.36,SoraNoWoto,,0000,0000,0000,,What are you doing?!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:21.36,0:13:24.57,SoraNoWoto,,0000,0000,0000,,Why did you come here in this typhoon?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:24.57,0:13:26.28,SoraNoWoto,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm protecting the eggplants!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:26.28,0:13:27.66,SoraNoWoto,,0000,0000,0000,,What are you saying?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:27.66,0:13:28.99,SoraNoWoto,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't be stupid!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:28.99,0:13:30.83,SoraNoWoto,,0000,0000,0000,,We're risking our lives because of you!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:30.83,0:13:32.83,SoraNoWoto,,0000,0000,0000,,No one asked you to do that!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:32.83,0:13:34.20,SoraNoWoto,,0000,0000,0000,,I never asked you to save me!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:35.00,0:13:36.62,SoraNoWoto,,0000,0000,0000,,What did you say?!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:36.62,0:13:38.38,SoraNoWoto,,0000,0000,0000,,Enough already!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:44.97,0:13:49.89,SoraNoWoto,,0000,0000,0000,,Listen, kids without parents need to be stronger than the other kids.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:50.57,0:13:53.77,SoraNoWoto,,0000,0000,0000,,Everyone will look down on you if you cause trouble.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:55.77,0:13:58.57,SoraNoWoto,,0000,0000,0000,,Not only you, but Yumina...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:59.73,0:14:01.86,SoraNoWoto,,0000,0000,0000,,They'll look down on her, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:02.32,0:14:03.86,SoraNoWoto,,0000,0000,0000,,Kureha...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:05.61,0:14:06.36,SoraNoWoto,,0000,0000,0000,,Okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:08.45,0:14:10.62,SoraNoWoto,,0000,0000,0000,,I know, because I'm an orphan too.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:11.70,0:14:14.24,SoraNoWoto,,0000,0000,0000,,Come on, let's get back.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:15.08,0:14:15.83,SoraNoWoto,,0000,0000,0000,,But...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:16.32,0:14:18.29,SoraNoWoto,,0000,0000,0000,,You're still complaining?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:18.29,0:14:19.83,SoraNoWoto,,0000,0000,0000,,Now, calm down.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:20.67,0:14:27.34,SoraNoWoto,,0000,0000,0000,,Something you grow with all your heart is as valuable as your life.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:30.00,0:14:32.96,SoraNoWoto,,0000,0000,0000,,These are big enough to eat.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:34.10,0:14:37.93,SoraNoWoto,,0000,0000,0000,,When pickled, they're absolutely delicious.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:41.27,0:14:43.19,SoraNoWoto,,0000,0000,0000,,Thank you, mister!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:43.73,0:14:45.10,SoraNoWoto,,0000,0000,0000,,Major...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:55.16,0:14:57.58,SoraNoWoto,,0000,0000,0000,,Seiya-kun is climbing up.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:08.80,0:15:10.84,SoraNoWoto,,0000,0000,0000,,Major, please go first!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:10.84,0:15:12.14,SoraNoWoto,,0000,0000,0000,,Sure...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:18.35,0:15:20.60,SoraNoWoto,,0000,0000,0000,,No, you go first.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:21.10,0:15:22.94,SoraNoWoto,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll watch your back.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:23.61,0:15:24.36,SoraNoWoto,,0000,0000,0000,,Roger!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:51.97,0:15:54.76,SoraNoWoto,,0000,0000,0000,,Both of them seem to be okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:55.26,0:15:56.04,SoraNoWoto,,0000,0000,0000,,But...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:57.47,0:15:59.56,SoraNoWoto,,0000,0000,0000,,They lost their means back up.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:00.18,0:16:03.31,SoraNoWoto,,0000,0000,0000,,This is the worst-case scenario.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:10.78,0:16:12.40,SoraNoWoto,,0000,0000,0000,,Thank you very much.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:12.40,0:16:13.57,SoraNoWoto,,0000,0000,0000,,D-Don't mention it.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:13.59,0:16:15.82,SoraNoWoto,,0000,0000,0000,,Our situation has worsened,
Dialogue: 0,0:16:16.78,0:16:19.33,SoraNoWoto,,0000,0000,0000,,but I'm with you, Major.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:20.54,0:16:23.33,SoraNoWoto,,0000,0000,0000,,I believe you'll be able to do something.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:26.13,0:16:27.09,SoraNoWoto,,0000,0000,0000,,You got it wrong...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:27.60,0:16:29.71,SoraNoWoto,,0000,0000,0000,,What? Did you say something?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:30.80,0:16:31.97,SoraNoWoto,,0000,0000,0000,,Nothing.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:36.14,0:16:38.35,SoraNoWoto,,0000,0000,0000,,Listen now, don't be afraid.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:38.35,0:16:41.73,SoraNoWoto,,0000,0000,0000,,You're with "Miracle Claus" now.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:41.73,0:16:42.98,SoraNoWoto,,0000,0000,0000,,I won't!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:44.27,0:16:45.73,SoraNoWoto,,0000,0000,0000,,The ground won't hold!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:46.15,0:16:47.52,SoraNoWoto,,0000,0000,0000,,It's eroding away.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:48.27,0:16:51.23,SoraNoWoto,,0000,0000,0000,,Dammit, this is why I hate kids!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:51.99,0:16:56.49,SoraNoWoto,,0000,0000,0000,,A kid that won't do what he's told should just be locked inside!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:56.49,0:16:57.18,SoraNoWoto,,0000,0000,0000,,Rio!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:58.53,0:17:00.24,SoraNoWoto,,0000,0000,0000,,What's the point of getting worked up?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:01.66,0:17:05.25,SoraNoWoto,,0000,0000,0000,,Those kids have always been looking up to you.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:06.79,0:17:09.50,SoraNoWoto,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm sorry, I said too much.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:09.50,0:17:13.26,SoraNoWoto,,0000,0000,0000,,B-But I'm sure they can do something.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:13.26,0:17:15.88,SoraNoWoto,,0000,0000,0000,,They say Claus-san brings miracles, after all.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:15.88,0:17:17.22,SoraNoWoto,,0000,0000,0000,,That's not true.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:19.05,0:17:23.27,SoraNoWoto,,0000,0000,0000,,He is neither the Desert Wolf nor Miracle Claus.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:23.27,0:17:28.06,SoraNoWoto,,0000,0000,0000,,He just happened to have a similar name and stature.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:29.40,0:17:33.65,SoraNoWoto,,0000,0000,0000,,Kureha got too exited and decided it by herself the first time they met.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:33.65,0:17:35.78,SoraNoWoto,,0000,0000,0000,,Since Claus doesn't speak much,
Dialogue: 0,0:17:36.15,0:17:39.95,SoraNoWoto,,0000,0000,0000,,he always missed his chance to clear up the misunderstanding.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:39.95,0:17:41.53,SoraNoWoto,,0000,0000,0000,,That's...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:41.53,0:17:46.47,SoraNoWoto,,0000,0000,0000,,Anyway, right now we need to think of a way for the courier who only has a long record of service,
Dialogue: 0,0:17:46.47,0:17:52.80,SoraNoWoto,,0000,0000,0000,,and the motivated yet inexperienced soldier, to get out of there.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:53.52,0:17:55.55,SoraNoWoto,,0000,0000,0000,,Give them rope.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:56.93,0:17:58.30,SoraNoWoto,,0000,0000,0000,,There's no foothold above them.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:59.34,0:18:02.81,SoraNoWoto,,0000,0000,0000,,The distance is too far if we were to throw it from here.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:02.81,0:18:06.77,SoraNoWoto,,0000,0000,0000,,If it's about throwing a rope from here,
Dialogue: 0,0:18:08.05,0:18:08.81,SoraNoWoto,,0000,0000,0000,,there's a way.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:10.48,0:18:18.15,SoraNoWoto,,0000,0000,0000,,The first time I met you, I thought that if my father were still alive, he'd look just like you.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:19.82,0:18:24.83,SoraNoWoto,,0000,0000,0000,,I always talk to everyone as if I know my father well,
Dialogue: 0,0:18:24.83,0:18:28.50,SoraNoWoto,,0000,0000,0000,,but the truth is I just heard about him from others,
Dialogue: 0,0:18:28.50,0:18:30.67,SoraNoWoto,,0000,0000,0000,,so I don't really know everything.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:30.67,0:18:34.59,SoraNoWoto,,0000,0000,0000,,By the time I was old enough to understand, he was already gone.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:34.59,0:18:35.88,SoraNoWoto,,0000,0000,0000,,Kureha...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:59.95,0:19:03.87,SoraNoWoto,,0000,0000,0000,,"Pay attention to your left."
Dialogue: 0,0:19:03.87,0:19:06.16,SoraNoWoto,,0000,0000,0000,,Heave-ho! Heave-ho!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:06.16,0:19:07.37,SoraNoWoto,,0000,0000,0000,,The Takemikazuchi!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:07.37,0:19:12.38,SoraNoWoto,,0000,0000,0000,,Heave-ho! Heave-ho!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:12.38,0:19:13.51,SoraNoWoto,,0000,0000,0000,,Halt!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:17.30,0:19:18.88,SoraNoWoto,,0000,0000,0000,,How is it, Noel-chan?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:19.59,0:19:22.34,SoraNoWoto,,0000,0000,0000,,The Linear Anchor Coil is functional.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:22.34,0:19:26.06,SoraNoWoto,,0000,0000,0000,,Targeting System, partially functional from B7 to F5.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:26.77,0:19:27.77,SoraNoWoto,,0000,0000,0000,,Begin targeting.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:35.57,0:19:36.27,SoraNoWoto,,0000,0000,0000,,It's possible.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:37.07,0:19:39.28,SoraNoWoto,,0000,0000,0000,,Prepare to fire the wire-anchor!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:39.28,0:19:40.78,SoraNoWoto,,0000,0000,0000,,Kanata, do it!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:40.78,0:19:41.78,SoraNoWoto,,0000,0000,0000,,Roger!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:51.96,0:19:52.79,SoraNoWoto,,0000,0000,0000,,It's coming!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:55.59,0:19:59.26,SoraNoWoto,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll protect you in your deceased father's stead!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:02.26,0:20:03.09,SoraNoWoto,,0000,0000,0000,,Roger.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:03.97,0:20:05.05,SoraNoWoto,,0000,0000,0000,,Major.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:07.76,0:20:08.56,SoraNoWoto,,0000,0000,0000,,Ready!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:09.02,0:20:09.56,SoraNoWoto,,0000,0000,0000,,Fire!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:16.31,0:20:17.11,SoraNoWoto,,0000,0000,0000,,Come on!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:19.82,0:20:20.61,SoraNoWoto,,0000,0000,0000,,Kureha!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:20.61,0:20:21.57,SoraNoWoto,,0000,0000,0000,,Major!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:29.79,0:20:31.12,SoraNoWoto,,0000,0000,0000,,Kureha-chan!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:31.12,0:20:32.54,SoraNoWoto,,0000,0000,0000,,Retract the anchor!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:32.54,0:20:33.08,SoraNoWoto,,0000,0000,0000,,Hurry!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:02.11,0:21:04.07,SoraNoWoto,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, Kureha...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:04.86,0:21:08.07,SoraNoWoto,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm gonna say this since we managed to survive.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:08.07,0:21:09.08,SoraNoWoto,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:09.08,0:21:10.95,SoraNoWoto,,0000,0000,0000,,You really are...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:12.50,0:21:14.54,SoraNoWoto,,0000,0000,0000,,...the man I looked up to, after all.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:28.01,0:21:31.53,SoraNoWoto,,0000,0000,0000,,A clear blue sky right after a typhoon, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:32.18,0:21:34.06,SoraNoWoto,,0000,0000,0000,,So you pulled it off, after all.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:34.06,0:21:35.94,SoraNoWoto,,0000,0000,0000,,I was honestly surprised.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:35.94,0:21:38.06,SoraNoWoto,,0000,0000,0000,,I didn't expect you to be able to do that.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:38.61,0:21:45.20,SoraNoWoto,,0000,0000,0000,,When I saw those eyes that believed in me, I was more afraid of crushing Kureha's dreams than of dying.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:46.03,0:21:49.53,SoraNoWoto,,0000,0000,0000,,That's why I could pull it off.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:50.83,0:21:53.45,SoraNoWoto,,0000,0000,0000,,In the end, I'm just a coward.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:54.20,0:21:55.71,SoraNoWoto,,0000,0000,0000,,That's not true!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:55.71,0:21:57.42,SoraNoWoto,,0000,0000,0000,,You were wonderful, Claus-san.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:59.38,0:22:00.59,SoraNoWoto,,0000,0000,0000,,Listen up, girly.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:01.13,0:22:05.26,SoraNoWoto,,0000,0000,0000,,What you see on the surface and what the person truly feels...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:05.26,0:22:07.88,SoraNoWoto,,0000,0000,0000,,are very different.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:08.38,0:22:13.01,SoraNoWoto,,0000,0000,0000,,The glasses called "admiration" are always blurry.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:13.01,0:22:18.19,SoraNoWoto,,0000,0000,0000,,You'll understand how hard it is someday, when you're looked at through those glasses.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:18.19,0:22:22.27,SoraNoWoto,,0000,0000,0000,,Could you at least stay until Kureha wakes up?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:23.11,0:22:25.11,SoraNoWoto,,0000,0000,0000,,Can you pass this on to Kureha?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:25.74,0:22:31.37,SoraNoWoto,,0000,0000,0000,,This is the best scar of honor in my entire life!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:15.80,0:24:19.93,SoraNoWoto,,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}Next episode: Departure - The First Snow.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:08.85,0:00:18.24,OP-TL,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2.2\fad(130,130)}The radiance of this sky will carry to your heart
Dialogue: 0,0:00:18.84,0:00:28.55,OP-TL,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2.2\fad(130,130)}The melody you dreamed of is like serenity
Dialogue: 0,0:00:28.55,0:00:33.54,OP-TL,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2.2\fad(130,130)}For your hands the dream is still far away, but
Dialogue: 0,0:00:33.54,0:00:38.54,OP-TL,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2.2\fad(130,130)}remember the voice so gentle
Dialogue: 0,0:00:38.55,0:00:51.23,OP-TL,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2.2\fad(130,130)}when someone sang the chord of happiness
Dialogue: 0,0:00:51.26,0:01:00.70,OP-TL,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2.2\fad(130,130)}The sound of the skies echoes high over all sadness
Dialogue: 0,0:01:00.70,0:01:11.34,OP-TL,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2.2\fad(130,130)}Everything reflected in your eyes is the real world
Dialogue: 0,0:01:11.34,0:01:20.68,OP-TL,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2.2\fad(130,130)}Not even the shedding of of tears can stop you here
Dialogue: 0,0:01:20.68,0:01:33.24,OP-TL,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2.2\fad(130,130)}We're playing tomorrow in the light that rains without end
Dialogue: 0,0:22:45.23,0:22:51.02,ED-TL,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(150,150)\blur2}Resonate the feelings of love and friendship
Dialogue: 0,0:22:51.02,0:22:54.11,ED-TL,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(150,150)\blur2}Let's perform the important things
Dialogue: 0,0:23:09.50,0:23:12.11,ED-TL,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(150,150)\blur2}I cried when I was happy
Dialogue: 0,0:23:15.25,0:23:18.06,ED-TL,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(150,150)\blur2}I laughed when I was hurt
Dialogue: 0,0:23:20.52,0:23:27.37,ED-TL,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(150,150)\blur2}But, they're all proof that I'm alive
Dialogue: 0,0:23:27.37,0:23:31.51,ED-TL,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(150,150)\blur2}Let's walk slowly
Dialogue: 0,0:23:31.51,0:23:33.36,ED-TL,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(150,150)\blur2}Everybody singing
Dialogue: 0,0:23:33.36,0:23:37.46,ED-TL,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(150,150)\blur2}Tell me what you truly want
Dialogue: 0,0:23:37.46,0:23:38.73,ED-TL,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(150,150)\blur2}You're just my friend
Dialogue: 0,0:23:38.73,0:23:44.89,ED-TL,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(150,150)\blur2}Even if love and friendship change over time
Dialogue: 0,0:23:41.94,0:23:44.89,ED-TL,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(150,150)\blur2\an1\3c&H5ECC69&}I know, You know little happy
Dialogue: 0,0:23:44.89,0:23:50.35,ED-TL,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(150,150)\blur2}I want them to echo forever
Dialogue: 0,0:23:47.89,0:23:50.89,ED-TL,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(150,150)\blur2\an1\3c&H5ECC69&}Can you hear my precious note?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:50.89,0:23:56.67,ED-TL,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(150,150)\blur2}Speaking endless words touched by love
Dialogue: 0,0:23:56.67,0:24:02.81,ED-TL,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(150,150)\blur2}This is our harmony
Dialogue: 0,0:24:02.83,0:24:07.44,ED-TL,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(150,150)\blur2}I can hear our harmony
